Body: At World Trip, we're always on the lookout for events to showcase our project to top tier investors and people who believe in our project. That's right - expect 110% diligence in whatever we do, and a proactive mindset to aim for a successful realization of our project goals. That is why we grabbed the opportunity to attend The Deal Makers in Singapore last week, a private investors' showcase organized by Far East Advisory.    And we're not like any other startup, literally. We got a MVP, 40+ beta testers ready, plus a dedicated team that, no matter what obstacles lie ahead, is ever ready to revolutionize the travel industry, and bring to you - the people - the power to bypass the middlemen so that you can connect directly with travelers worldwide.    Our enthusiasm is palpable. You can feel it when you are browsing our active social media channels and when you are looking at our pictures from Principality 2018, organised by Principal Strategic last November. We're out there, pitching, never giving up till World Trip Singapore becomes your go-to companion for travelling.  Want to learn more about us? Don't hesitate. Author: WTS
Title: [ANN-PRE ICO]World Trip Singapore : Bridging Cultures - One eXperience at a Time
Body: Our team is happy to announce that Sheikh Harrith, CEO of Travel Nation, is joining World Trip Singapore as Chief Marketing Officer.  As CEO of Travel Nation, Sheikh has experience in setting up and partnerships of corporations in the travel and blockchain industries. Also a blockchain and travel enthusiast, Sheikh’s mission has always been to revolutionize the travel industry with blockchain. He has since merged his passion with his profession and combined the best of both worlds in Travel Nation.  Sheikh is also one of the biggest travel influencers in Instagram with over 90,000 followers around the globe. His Instagram channel is regularly visited and appreciated by over millions of people per week worldwide.  With his growth mindset and innovative drive, World Trip Singapore will benefit from the insights that Sheikh has to offer to help accelerate World Trip Singapore’s status as one of the most revolutionary blockchain-powered travel platforms.  Learn more at: https://medium.com/worldtrip-sg/sheikh-harrith-ceo-at-travel-nation-media-joins-world-trip-singapore-as-chief-marketing-officer-ff61d5e1a8a?fbclid=IwAR2djfmeSXdMlMR_or_dOX1NKjq8Z7ZE39S7YlGctfWG2QPb9AdhC_EGIyk

Author: WTS
Title: [ANN-PRE ICO]World Trip Singapore : Bridging Cultures - One eXperience at a Time
Body: Did you know?  According to Wegoplaces' Solo Travel Safety Report 2019, Singapore is the SAFEST destination for solo travel. If you like to travel alone, you know where to go!  Here are the 10 safest locations for solo travel with index score (the higher the score, the greater proportion of the population reports feeling safe):  1. Singapore (97)  2. Norway (93)  3. Iceland (93)  4. Finland (93)  5. Uzbekistan (91)  6. Hong Kong (91)  7. Switzerland (90)  8. Canada (90)  9. Indonesia (89)  10. Denmark (88)  What does this data mean for you?  We encourage everyone to travel alone at least once in their life. Because once you take the leap to go alone, you have to make decisions on the spot and overcome your fears, hence discovering your true self and how much you are actually capable of. You will also gain valuable skills and grow into a more confident person!  So go ahead, pack your luggage, and we will see you in Singapore soon.

Body: HoweyCoins is actually a mock website done by The United States Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) highlighting the dangers of investing in ICOs.  We believe that World Trip passes the Howey Test. Our digital token (WTXT) we’re selling is not considered to be a security, do not represent shares in our company, or pay holders with dividends. Our token acts as a settlement, payment and transaction currency for the WTS platform. You may visit our website https://wtxt.io/ see the advantages WTXT holders have. We also don't target the whole travel industry and we don't guarantee profits from investing in our coin.

Author: WTS
Title: [ANN-PRE ICO]World Trip Singapore : Bridging Cultures - One eXperience at a Time
Body: Hello guys, what's up! You may have watched our explainer video or even read the whitepaper which contains about 40 pages. Nevertheless, the best way to get the gist of the project is to check an interactive prototype! https://tinyurl.com/wtsprototype  We’ve done our best to make it really simple to use and, at the same time, to show our key features at work. Here’s what you can do while exploring the demo:  - Search a destination or attraction (in this case Sentosa) - See a list of tour guides for Sentosa - Click on one of the tour guides (Amelia) to see their ratings, bio, and itineraries - Chat with the tour guide using AirChat - See the account section where you can find the history of your bookings, edit your profile and use your WTXT wallet and rewards  Hope you’ll enjoy this experience and all comments are most welcome!  WTXT are currently in presale. You can get in now with 40% bonus before it is sold out at www.wtxt.io  And we are going to release our beta app soon... but it's only available in Singapore. So if you are a Singaporean or Singapore PR, and you'd like to join our mission to create unforgettable travel experiences, please sign up now at https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScCPANJ03QlB5hUO54HPfXdGKx2GHKdIRybw_sRhcBNNYq13Q/viewform, no strings attached!

Author: WTS
Title: [ANN-PRE ICO]World Trip Singapore : Bridging Cultures - One eXperience at a Time
Body: Presale promotion is now on! 40% additional Tokens if you purchase WTXT! Get them while stock last!  Minimum contribution = 1 ETH  https://wtxt.io/  World Trip Singapore Airdrop/Bounty campaign has ENDED  Our airdrop program has come to an end. We are amazed by the overwhelming support received from all participants. Thank you for your support and encouragement for the World Trip Singapore project!  We had distributed all WTXT to all registered ETH wallets.  Read the FAQ: https://medium.com/worldtrip-sg/the-world-trip-singapore-airdrop-bounty-program-has-ended-811c0b0eb352  About  In the midst of travelling needs shifting from “the material” to “the experience”, we want to focus on that state of growing content surrounding experiences. The way tourists look for information, on such things as services and restaurants found only in that country, and how they have fun during travel, is changing.  A growing number of people are no longer satisfied with packages tour companies offer; Japan too has websites providing experiences or concierge and consulting services.  Our plan is develop our services first in Asia, where the number of tourists are growing in recent years, then to Europe and America, expanding the WTS platform globally. Once guests use the platform, it provides a space for those guests to become local hosts. By combining the information of what only locals know and the skills of a host and communicating it, citizens of the world will pay attention and make a reservation if compelled to participate or experience such things. The arrangement is complete once the host guides the tourists to the local hot spots.  Whether it’ s a unique plan that only local people can do, an experience that’ s been introduced on the WTS platform website, or niche activities not yet known online, WTS is a tool that offers a new dimension to travel.  Solution  Decentralized social travel platform that combines artificial intelligence and user generated content to provide travellers with a one-stop service for booking and sharing travel experiences. Hybrid between an Online Travel Agent (OTA) and social networking (SNS) platform for travellers. Powered by the Word Trip Xperience token (WTXT)  created for the exchange of travel services, airlocker’s service, and future duty-free shops around the world.  Still curious? Take a look at our promotional video.     Wonder how it will work on your phone? Take a look at our Prototype:  http://demo.wtxt.io                Tokens Sale  Private Sale (1st October 2018 - 31st December 2018) 1 ETH = 800 WTXT Issued tokens = 20,000,000 WTXT  Presale(1st January 2019 - 28th February 2019) 1 ETH = 400 WTXT Issued tokens = 10,000,000 WTXT  Public Sale (1st March 2019 - 30th April 2019) 1 ETH = 200 WTXT Issued tokens = 5,000,000 WTXT  Minimum contribution = 1 ETH  Buy now and ENJOY 40% PROMOTION: https://wtxt.io/  Check us out here for more details:  Whitepaper: https://wtxt.io/wp-content/uploads/WTS_whitepaper_eng.pdf  Attended Blockchain Conferences: https://icoholder.com/en/press-releases/principality-2018?fbclid=IwAR31KWQzpOIJf8WIRcYCLK9G7XpNgryMPTV5BDc8fNyjWPCOcWqIhdw6_5s  Press Releases: https://www.issuewire.com/world-trip-singapore-to-introduce-a-brand-new-travel-experience-with-blockchain-powered-platform-1621629997564046 https://medium.com/swlh/world-trip-singapore-to-introduce-a-brand-new-travel-experience-with-blockchain-powered-platform-410d2b13b563  Social Media: Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/wtxtsg Twitter: https://twitter.com/WorldTripSG Telegram: https://t.me/worldtrip_sg Github: https://github.com/WorldTripSingapore Medium: https://medium.com/worldtrip-sg BitcoinTalk: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=5081373.0  ICO Listings: ICOBENCH: https://icobench.com/ico/world-trip-singapore ICOHolder: https://icoholder.com/en/world-trip-singapore-27792 LISTICO: https://www.listico.io/ico/world-trip-singapore    Presale promotion is now on! 40% additional tokens if you purchase WTXT!
